WEBVTT

00:07:28.614 --> 00:07:32.655
It remained a conjecture --
Kelvin's conjecture.

00:07:32.655 --> 00:07:38.177
The world, as you know, then split into
Kelvinists and anti-Kelvinists

00:07:38.177 --> 00:07:39.599
(Laughter)

00:07:39.599 --> 00:07:43.496
until a hundred or so years later,

00:07:46.203 --> 00:07:50.072
someone found a better structure.

00:07:50.917 --> 00:07:56.026
Weaire and Phelan
found this little thing over here --

00:07:56.026 --> 00:07:57.665
(Laughter) --

00:07:57.665 --> 00:08:01.209
this structure to which they gave
the very clever name